For code review tasks in this repo, use
[docs/ai/code-review.md](docs/ai/code-review.md) as the shared source
of truth.

For documentation audits, doc-heavy changes, or docs-focused review, also use
[docs/ai/check-docs.md](docs/ai/check-docs.md).

Accepted code-review scope arguments:

- `diff` (default)
- `full`
- file / directory / glob

When this wrapper and the shared doc differ, follow the shared doc.
